					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Teddy Wayne</h4>
												<p>Teddy Wayne, the author of <em>Apartment, Loner, The Love Song of Jonny Valentine,</em> and <em>Kapitoil,</em> is the winner of a Whiting Writers’ Award and an NEA Fellowship as well as a finalist for the Young Lions Fiction Award, PEN/Bingham Prize, and Dayton Literary Peace Prize. He writes regularly for <em>The New Yorker, The New York Times, Vanity Fair, McSweeney’s,</em> and elsewhere. He lives in New York.</p>
					</div>
